    <!-- Apex access for the @AuraEnabled controllers behind the dashboard and the
         embedded schedule manager, so a full admin assigned only this set (without
         profile-level Apex access) can use both UIs. Class-level security is enforced
         only at the LWC entry point, so downstream classes need no entry. -->
